# Force LF on checkout on every platform (crlfcheckout, C.1.3.2). Prevents Windows
# autocrlf from dirtying the working tree (which blocks `git checkout`/clone-script
# updates) and keeps text byte-identical to the commit on every platform.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.exe binary
*.zip binary
